---
import MainLayout from "@/layouts/MainLayout.astro";

const pageTitle = "Terms of Service | WinFlowz";
---

<MainLayout
  title={pageTitle}
  lang="en"
  structuredData={{
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "WebPage",
    "@id": "https://winflowz.com/terms",
    "url": "https://winflowz.com/terms",
    "name": "Terms of Service | WinFlowz",
    "description": "Terms of Service for WinFlowz digital productivity tools and services.",
    "inLanguage": "en"
  }}
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 text-neutral-900 dark:text-white">Terms of Service</h1>

    <p class="text-sm mb-4 text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">Last updated: December 15, 2024</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">1. Introduction</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">These Terms of Service govern your use of WinFlowz's digital products and services, including but not limited to Obsidian plugins (CreatorFlowz, RSSFlowz, PluginFlowz, MediaFlowz, EditorFlowz, MailingFlowz, LinkFlowz), Chrome extensions (TubeFlowz), and associated training services.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">2. License and Usage Rights</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">2.1. WinFlowz grants you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable license to use the purchased products for personal use.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">2.2. The "FlowzSuite for Obsidian" pack includes lifetime access to all current plugins with their updates.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">2.3. Individual plugins and extensions may be subject to separate licensing terms.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">3. Intellectual Property</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">3.1. All products, including source code, designs, and documentation, remain the exclusive property of WinFlowz.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">3.2. You may not redistribute, resell, or modify the products without explicit written permission.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">4. API Usage and Data Processing</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">4.1. Some products require third-party API keys (YouTube, Unsplash, Pexels, etc.). You are responsible for obtaining and managing these keys.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">4.2. Data processing is performed locally on your device. Winflowz does not collect or store your personal data.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">5. Training and Services</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">5.1. Training sessions and consultations are subject to availability.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">5.2. Cancellations must be made at least 24 hours in advance for a full refund.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">6. Refund Policy</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">6.1. Digital products come with a 30-day satisfaction guarantee.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">6.2. Training service refunds are subject to the cancellation policy.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">7. Liability Limitations</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">7.1. Products are provided "as is" without warranty of any kind.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">7.2. Winflowz is not liable for damages resulting from the use of our products.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">8. Updates and Modifications</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">8.1. Winflowz reserves the right to update products and these terms at any time.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">8.2. Users will be notified of significant changes to terms or functionality.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">9. Support and Maintenance</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">9.1. Technical support is provided only through official channels.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">9.2. Response times are not guaranteed but typically within 48 hours.</p>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4 text-neutral-800 dark:text-neutral-200">10. Termination</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">10.1. Winflowz reserves the right to terminate services in case of abuse or violation of these terms.</p>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 dark:text-neutral-400">10.2. Users may terminate their use of services at any time.</p>

    <p class="mt-8 text-sm text-neutral-500 dark:text-neutral-400">For any questions regarding these terms, please contact us at support@winflowz.com</p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
